    "description_long": "A group of three red apples is arranged on a round white plate. Two apples are whole, each with a short brown stem, and one apple is sliced in half, revealing its pale interior and visible seeds. A single wedge-shaped slice is also present, showing the crisp white flesh and red skin. The apples have a slightly glossy surface with subtle yellow highlights near the stem. The plate is smooth and flat, providing a clean backdrop for the fruit. The overall appearance is fresh and inviting, suitable for a kitchen, picnic, or urban park setting.",
